&lt;p>&lt;img src="/imgs/img-lazy-loading.gif" data-src="https://pic.rmb.bdstatic.com/bjh/down/bb19f3787d8a2d59485725481085abe0.png" alt="" />&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>医生，请不要给我开中成药 敢对医生说这句话，能帮你节省85%的医药费。</title><link>/post/%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%99%E6%88%91%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%88%90%E8%8D%AF-%E6%95%A2%E5%AF%B9%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%A5%E8%AF%9D%E8%83%BD%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%8185%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BB%E8%8D%AF%E8%B4%B9/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/post/%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B7%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%99%E6%88%91%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%88%90%E8%8D%AF-%E6%95%A2%E5%AF%B9%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%A5%E8%AF%9D%E8%83%BD%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%8185%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BB%E8%8D%AF%E8%B4%B9/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>“医生，请不要给我开中成药。”&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>医生，请不要给我开中成药 敢对医生说这句话，能帮你节省85%的医药费。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我的读者U先生，就是因为太过儒雅，没好意思对医生说这句话，白白浪费掉了450元的药费。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>5月7日，U先生因为眼睛不适，经同事推荐，前往北京某著名中西医结合三甲医院就诊。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>这批仁丹，汞含量超欧盟标准9.7万倍</title><link>/post/%E8%BF%99%E6%89%B9%E4%BB%81%E4%B8%B9%E6%B1%9E%E5%90%AB%E9%87%8F%E8%B6%85%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E6%A0%87%E5%87%869.7%E4%B8%87%E5%80%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/post/%E8%BF%99%E6%89%B9%E4%BB%81%E4%B8%B9%E6%B1%9E%E5%90%AB%E9%87%8F%E8%B6%85%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E6%A0%87%E5%87%869.7%E4%B8%87%E5%80%8D/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="/imgs/img-lazy-loading.gif" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fO6zWA5AIeF3EiczqFrowWVKsfsaxyEfkS5RKynDtjHaXuhHfoicfKz8qM7hEqI4x6htOAibp0lX646wQpItLm5ZQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&amp;amp;tp=wxpic&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;amp;wx_co=1" alt="图片" />&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="这批仁丹汞含量超欧盟标准97万倍">这批仁丹，汞含量超欧盟标准9.7万倍
